title: Peepin It Real T Shirt Happy Easter Bunny Egg Hunt Funny T-Shirt
features: • Solid colors: 100% Cotton; Heather Grey: 90% Cotton, 10% Polyester; All Other Heathers: 50% Cotton, 50% Polyester
• Imported
• Machine wash cold with like colors, dry low heat

• Peepin It Real is the perfect easter 2022 t shirt for kids women & men that love to celebrate easter sunday with family & friends.Wear this funny easter tshirt for toddlers & adults while you go egg hunting,dye eggs or chill with your favorite bunnies.

• On easter day grab your easter basket,put on your easter face mask,wear this cute easter bunny tee outfit for boys & girls and hip & hop while egg hunting with mom,dad,grandma,grandpa,auntie,uncle and find all the easter eggs hidden by the easter bunny.
• Lightweight, Classic fit, Double-needle sleeve and bottom hem
